headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock with Solid Fundamentals and 2 We Brush Off
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.

headline: Delta CEO on new nonstop route from Atlanta to Riyadh: “I believe it’s going to gain popularity quickly.”
summary: Delta Air Lines CEO Ed Bastian discussed plans for a new direct route from Atlanta to Riyadh while speaking at the Fortune Global Forum.
